  "designPrinciples": [
    "Presence Over Transaction — Remittances are acts of presence. Design should honor the emotional weight of sending money to family.",
    "Progressive Capability — The product should make users stronger over time — more knowledgeable, more confident, more capable.",
    "Meet People Where They Are — Start simple, reveal complexity gradually. Progressive disclosure over feature overload.",
    "Grow With Users — From first send to comprehensive financial management. The system expands as users are ready.",
    "Celebrate Growth — Acknowledge milestones and learning, not just task completion."
